oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Nashville Tracks #3 - Program Music - Biff Collie
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Recording of program music for Biff Collie's radio program; the tape is the third of the Nashville Tracks collection. Tracks performed by an unidentified band at Woodland Sound Studio A.
